- cs.IR (Information Retrieval): The paper deals with summarizing social media texts, which can be seen as a form of information retrieval. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning): The proposed model is a neural network-based approach, which falls under the scope of cs.LG. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper deals with improving the performance of a machine learning model for text summarization, which falls under the scope of cs.AI. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing): The proposed model is a neural network-based approach, which falls under the scope of cs.NE.
